==English==

===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[cornea tela]]'', horny tissue, from ''[[cornu]]'', horn

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /kɔː(r)ˈniə/
*[[SAMPA]]: /kO:(r)"ni@/

===Noun===
'''cornea''' (''plural'' '''corneas''')
# {{anatomy}} The transparent layer forming the front of the [[eye]].

